# Python bytecode caches (Phase 15 added .github/scripts/update_version.py
# + tests/test_update_version.py; their __pycache__ dirs were being picked
# up by beta-build.yml's stefanzweifel/git-auto-commit-action step and
# committed to origin/beta). Ignore the .pyc artifacts globally so the
# version-bump auto-commit only carries the intended version.h diff.
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
